room_title: Escape room "The Hillbilly Still" by Cloak and Dagger Escape Rooms Wildwood in Cape May
room_description: Well, My old granny Millie is out on bender somewhere. Aint no one seen her for days. But we gotta get her still a-runnin so’s we can fill that big order for that city slicker. But you know ole granny….she done HID all the ingredients to her Moonshine maker! If we don’t get that still pumping out that white lightning, that city slicker is gonna be really mad and there’s no telling what he might do. He’ll be here an in a half hour to check on our progress…..we gotta show him that that there shine is a-flowin!! Cmon, there stranger…give us a hand will ya!
